CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817079
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FSo why is the conflict pushing up
OL,7,Fenergy prices, can we expect petrol
OL,8,Fand diesel prices to go up, and what
OL,9,Fother areas of life in the UK may be
OL,10,Feffected? ITV News explains.
OL,12,FWhy is this happening?
OL,14,FOil markets are influenced by several
OL,15,Fglobal factors, including economic
OL,16,Fgrowth, supply and demand, and
OL,17,Fgeopolitics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
