CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817079
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FIn Qatar, strikes on the energy
OL,7,Fcompany QatarEnergy have led it to
OL,8,Fstop all production of liquified
OL,9,Fnatural gas (LNG), which has reduced
OL,10,Fshort-term supply by almost a fifth
OL,11,Fand sent global prices rising. Some
OL,12,Fcentral banks predict that this will
OL,13,Freduce LNG supply by around 19%.
OL,15,FLNG is used for domestic heating,
OL,16,Fcooking, and petrol and diesel, and so
OL,17,Fthis is expected to have a significant
OL,18,Fimpact on those costs.
OL,20,FWhat does this mean for my energy
OL,21,Fbills?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817079
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FHigher energy prices will ultimately
OL,7,Ffilter through to consumer and
OL,8,Fproducer prices, particularly for
OL,9,Feconomies that rely heavily on oil
OL,10,Fimports from the Middle East.
OL,12,FThe UK imports oil and LNG from
OL,13,Fvarious places, including the US and
OL,14,FNorway, as well as from the Middle
OL,15,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817079
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FBut a global increase in the cost of
OL,7,Fimporting oil will push up demand and
OL,8,Fcosts on all energy sources, including
OL,9,Falternatives, which could ultimately
OL,10,Fleave households paying more for
OL,11,Fenergy costs.
OL,13,FThis is because wholesale gas prices
OL,14,Ffeed into electricity prices and how
OL,15,Fmuch it costs to heat homes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
