OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817079
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the money saving expert
OL,7,FMartin Lewis has told customers of
OL,8,Fsome energy firms that now is the best
OL,9,Ftime to switch their energy tariffs
OL,10,Fgiven the current surge in prices.
OL,12,FWriting on X, Lewis said: "Important:
OL,13,FIf you can get off the Energy Price
OL,14,FCap right now, you should & urgently!"
OL,16,FHow will this impact petrol and diesel
OL,17,Fprices?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
