OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FCrude oil, like that that passes
OL,7,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz, is a key
OL,8,Fingredient in petrol and diesel
OL,9,Fmeaning it could soon cost more to
OL,10,Fproduce fuel, pushing up prices at the
OL,11,Fpumps.
OL,13,FThe motoring company AA says prices
OL,14,Fwill "inevitably increase" in the
OL,15,Fcoming weeks but stressed there was
OL,16,F"no need for drivers to break their
OL,17,Frefueling routine" because it takes
OL,18,Ftime for higher wholesale costs to
OL,19,Ffilter through to the pump.
OL,26,@vD@FOUvD@ZO]xD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
