OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817079
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FSimilarly, the RAC said while the
OL,7,FMiddle East conflict has the potential
OL,8,Fto increase fuel costs, it is not a
OL,9,Fcertainty: "The oil price would have
OL,10,Fto rise significantly and stay that
OL,11,Fway for some time to have a dramatic
OL,12,Feffect".
OL,14,FWill my weekly shop go up?
OL,16,FPossibly. Much of it comes back to
OL,17,Fsurging oil prices.
OL,26,@qD@LOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
