OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817080
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FAs well as energy prices, several
OL,7,Fmortgage lenders have signalled they
OL,8,Fwill increase their rates, with others
OL,9,Fexpected to follow suit amid changing
OL,10,Fmarket conditions.
OL,12,FHSBC UK will increase some of the
OL,13,Fmortgage rates it is offering from
OL,14,FFriday, including for first-time
OL,15,Fbuyers, home movers, people re-
OL,16,Fmortgaging and buy-to-let landlords.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
