PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772817080
OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,FNationwide Building Society is also
OL,7,Fpushing up some mortgage rates it is
OL,8,Foffering from Friday, including for
OL,9,Fsome first-time buyers, home movers
OL,10,Fand people switching and remortgaging.
OL,12,FCoventry Building Society is also set
OL,13,Fto increase its mortgage rates on
OL,14,FMonday.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, Moneyfacts said some
OL,17,Flenders had already pushed pause on
OL,18,Fplanned mortgage rate cuts, amid wider
OL,19,Feconomic and global uncertainties as
OL,20,Fthe conflict in the Middle East
OL,21,Funfolds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
