OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,F"Because fixed mortgage pricing is
OL,7,Fclosely linked to swap rates, this
OL,8,Fsudden market movement risks halting
OL,9,Fthe recent momentum towards lower
OL,10,Fmortgage rates just as borrower
OL,11,Fconfidence had begun to build ahead of
OL,12,Fan anticipated rate cut.
OL,14,F"It serves as a stark reminder that
OL,15,Fmortgage costs are not driven solely
OL,16,Fby domestic policy decisions.
