OL,3,CHow could conflict in the Middle East
OL,4,Caffect your bills at home?
OL,6,F"Global geopolitical events move
OL,7,Fmarkets, markets move swap rates, and
OL,8,Fswap rates ultimately shape the deals
OL,9,Favailable to borrowers ` all while the
OL,10,Fworld watches deeply troubling events
OL,11,Funfold."
